data.description: Come see this amazingly well maintained Pool Home in SE Cape. When you pull into the driveway, you will see the homes front porch with landscaping. Out back in the Privacy Fenced yard, enjoy swimming in the Heated In Ground pool or sit and relax in the screened porch. Inside, check out the updated kitchen with Solid surface counter tops, tile backsplash and Stainless Steel appliances. Both bathrooms have tiled showers with glass doors. This home features also include: New roof 2017, New A/C 2017 and Plumbing 2017. Make sure to add this one to your list.
